title: [FS2004] UK2000 Stansted xtreme
description:
Fs2004/FS9 UK2000 Stansted V3.1

Here is Stansted Extreme for Fs2004.

-------------INSTALL

Extract the file into your 'Addon Scenery' Folder and copy the 'effects' foler into 

your MAIN FS2004 folder.(Insert and Overwrite if asked)

Register the Szenerie in Fs2004 as usual.(setup-Options.exe not working)


That's it!


In the Options folder you can turn on/off the static Vehicles and some other things..

--------------

If something isn't working correctly or you still have questions, let me know and leave a comment.
